title: Tee Set
description:
Sorry this is only MP3, some tracks have Rumble on them, 
like the Turntable Kind, all in all I wish I had this in 
Flac, I hate MP3, but having these tracks in any format
is a joy. R.I.P., Peter Tetteroo and words can't say how
much the rest of these guys also had an influence on me,
Dill Bennink, Ray Fenwick, Ferry Lever, Joop Blom. 
Franklin Madjid, and last but not least, Hans Van Eijck.
 If you're reading this from Heaven Peter, you can't
punch me now, so I'd just like to say, I never knew
a Dutch Guy could sound like Otis Redding till I heard
you
